        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "As a mortal you delved into the minds of the criminally insane as a psychologist.Little did you know that your research hospital was actually just a facade for the Tremere of Miami. When the Sabbat came to lay waste to the Chantry, you were one of many who were embraced to serve as shock troops in their final assault on the mystically warded lair.  You have only a few fleeting memories of that night, though you're told that the Chantry was destroyed and that you drank the heart's blood of atleast one of the Tremere who stood their ground. As a Ventrue Antitribu you've had to prove yourself constantly and you've perfected the art of psychologically manipualting others for your benefit. You wrested control of your pack in 1996 by goading your pack leader into Monomacy with one of the Bishops of Detroit. Since then you've carefully cultivated and pruned pack members until you've arrived at the perfect combination of lap dogs, yes men and craven lick spittles.  Only Abigal Tillinghast has been in the pack longer than you and she remains your greatest challenge and prize. You know that a great power resides in her mind, with it you've developed the pack's Ignoblis Ritae that has allowed everyone in the pack to unburden their souls when needed. You long to fully understand her powers, but her mind is a a dangerous place to explore with Telepathy and you loathe the idea of trusting anyone you don't control with the secret of her power."
        ],
        [
